{"tid":91543,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【報館的錯】迎雞年黃大仙警示　香港運程連續兩載下下籤","createTime":"2017-01-23T02:46:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-23T07:34:20.000Z","uid":73262,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c406a31d1afa3d7ad59018befec0fde42c3b70c3","tid":91543,"uid":73262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T02:46:18.000Z","msg":"猴年象徵靈活有轉變，可是香港今年愈變愈困境。送猴迎雞，<span style=\"color: red;\">東方報業集團</span>按照習俗到黃大仙祠求籤問卜，仙師再賜香港運程一支下下籤「朱買臣分妻」，為連續兩年在同一卜題求得下下籤，籤文「夫妻反目兩分離」預示官民對立加劇，社會爭拗多，發展停滯不前已成覆水難收定局，港人必須如讀書人朱買臣一樣靠自己努力，自求多福，捱過農曆7月後方有轉機。 （省略一萬字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n我深信 絕對係間報館嘅問題"},{"pid":"59087917baf5c634e644e6861eb925a13ddbecdc","tid":91543,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T02:49:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12c237557979ca55fae5da009bae32b8ae251ffb","tid":91543,"uid":54502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T02:51:44.000Z","msg":"你憑咩野幫香港求籤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c49ecd5c15c76f543bd97fb6b92a1d51ba2c6d89","tid":91543,"uid":4964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T02:53:52.000Z","msg":"同中國分離？"},{"pid":"15d16ec4f61430bd359f21caf945f7eba72994a1","tid":91543,"uid":59206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T04:49:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同中國分離？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊撚個同中國兩夫妻"},{"pid":"fb63ad2b5488ec4ab843b15ee79611db811b16b8","tid":91543,"uid":38666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T04:56:31.000Z","msg":"因管理不善而接二連三抽出下下籤的東方集業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f4c6c5a3556b97fefb156753f5d5860255b10b5","tid":91543,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T05:07:51.000Z","msg":"睇黎因航會大賺, 貪曾會冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4ec62b13b159efad70c47ab70912d09942d0bbb","tid":91543,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T05:11:51.000Z","msg":"侵侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55ee64d1ddd10e47c4d8a397a64321e9f7839c00","tid":91543,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T07:21:32.000Z","msg":"第七十四靈籤：朱買臣分妻<br />\n求籤吉凶：下下靈籤<br />\n<br />\n算命籤詩：<br />\n回憶當年運蹇時 夫妻反目兩分離<br />\n名題雁塔歸來後 復水馬頭時否悲<br />\n<br />\n朱買臣，漢朝一位讀書人，本是貧寒之人，妻子不願意跟他挨餓一世，提出離婚。後來，朱買臣當了大官，妻子要求復合，朱買臣把一盆水潑在地上說：你能把這些水都收回到盆里，我們就復合吧！這就是復水難收的典故了。"},{"pid":"7239073eec579ffbe386b425e308e85857b179e3","tid":91543,"uid":37475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T07:34:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同中國分離？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊撚個同中國兩夫妻</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n台/港"}]}